    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292730/extras/9c13ea829b668dd48eaf8e53cf3b6746.poster.avif?t=1771442160\" width=768 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292730/extras/9c13ea829b668dd48eaf8e53cf3b6746.webm?t=1771442160\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292730/extras/9c13ea829b668dd48eaf8e53cf3b6746.mp4?t=1771442160\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A mysterious figure draws you into the game. Price: death. Executioner: you. You have dice in your hand and the consequences of this game on your shoulders. Act, predict, observe, and above all... cheat? How long will you last before your conscience takes your minds away? How long will you last before you throw away your values? Do you think you are capable of making sacrifices in the name of honor? The time of trial has come. Even if the die has been cast, let your decisions determine you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292730/extras/bd0e4883345df93c0c268b77bc25cdee.poster.avif?t=1771442160\" width=768 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292730/extras/bd0e4883345df93c0c268b77bc25cdee.webm?t=1771442160\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292730/extras/bd0e4883345df93c0c268b77bc25cdee.mp4?t=1771442160\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The die is cast</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your fate has been sealed, hasn't it? Observe your surroundings, look for solutions, develop a strategy, try to change the outcome of the roll to achieve your goals.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292730/extras/d17cf1b4a1c2fd05d765aec2dcc5e908.poster.avif?t=1771442160\" width=768 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292730/extras/d17cf1b4a1c2fd05d765aec2dcc5e908.webm?t=1771442160\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292730/extras/d17cf1b4a1c2fd05d765aec2dcc5e908.mp4?t=1771442160\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >There will come an end for everyone</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And it will be whatever you decide with fate. Will it be a happy one, and if so, for whom? Is it possible to arrange the turns in such a way as to save yourself and the world? You have to judge it for yourself and find the one that lets you sleep in peace.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292730/extras/b55c6d5b26c842440095b83bc68f7271.poster.avif?t=1771442160\" width=768 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292730/extras/b55c6d5b26c842440095b83bc68f7271.webm?t=1771442160\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292730/extras/b55c6d5b26c842440095b83bc68f7271.mp4?t=1771442160\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >It's a problem you're here</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Alone. Up in the air. In the midst of explosions. With decisions to be made. With an open question: what next? No one to help you. No hints. No UI. Fully immersed in a life-and-death game.</p>",
